messages.content: promptLAB-ComfyUI is a custom node or extension for ComfyUI that provides connection nodes for API requests and fully supports promptLAB.
Does promptLAB-ComfyUI support all features of promptLAB?
Yes, promptLAB-ComfyUI fully supports promptLAB, allowing users to leverage its functionality within the ComfyUI environment.
What type of requests can be made using promptLAB-ComfyUI?
promptLAB-ComfyUI allows users to make API requests using its connection nodes, enabling integration with external services and data sources.
Is promptLAB-ComfyUI a standalone application or an extension for ComfyUI?
promptLAB-ComfyUI is an extension or custom node for ComfyUI, not a standalone application.
What is the main purpose of promptLAB-ComfyUI?
The main purpose of promptLAB-ComfyUI is to provide connection nodes for API requests within the ComfyUI environment while fully supporting promptLAB functionality.
Can promptLAB-ComfyUI be used without ComfyUI?
No, promptLAB-ComfyUI is designed to be used within the ComfyUI environment as an extension or custom node.
How does promptLAB-ComfyUI enhance the functionality of ComfyUI?

promptLAB-ComfyUI enhances the functionality of ComfyUI by providing connection nodes for API requests and fully supporting promptLAB, allowing users to integrate external services and data sources into their projects.
